childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0An ancient tree...^$1A deep forest...^$2The goddess of the sand...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Link's Pocket...^$3An immense cavern...^$4The belly of a deity...^$5A vast lake...^$6A high mountain...^$7The house of the dead...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to collect&6 Spiritual Stones and Medallions.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be hidden somewhere %rinside&its castle%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: You'll never deflect my bolts of&energy with your sword, then shoot&me with those Light Arrows you&happen to have.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from %ra&high mountain%w!
lightArrowHintLoc: Fire Temple Boulder Maze Shortcut Chest
sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%ra high mountain%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%ra deep forest%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Damp√©
gregText: By the way, if you're interested,&I saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g Zora's Domain%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
sariaText: Did you feel the %gsurge of&magic%w recently? A mysterious&bird told me it came from %gDesert&Colossus%w.^You should check that place out,&@!$C
